  "title": "Bar Supervisor (up to $4,000 | Italian Posh Restaurant)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Oversee daily bar operations, including opening, closing, and shift coordination.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and serve alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages according to established standards.</p></li><li><p>Maintain bar hygiene, cleanliness, and safety compliance at all times.</p></li><li><p>Manage inventory, stock levels, and wastage; ensure timely replenishment.</p></li><li><p>Liaise with suppliers for orders, deliveries, and product updates.</p></li><li><p>Guide and support bar staff to ensure consistent service quality.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements:</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Strong bartending skills with solid knowledge of classic cocktails.</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in a bar or restaurant, preferably in a supervisory capacity.</p></li><li><p>Good communication, leadership ability, and attention to detail.</p></li><li><p>Responsible, independent, and able to handle operations during peak hours.</p></li></ul><p>Tyson Jay Management Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 24C2479</p><p>Ivan Lim | EA Personnel No.: R1109856</p>",
